1. Click "Login" in the nav bar
2. Verify you can enter Name and Email into a form
3. Verify there is a button to click in order to login
4. Enter valid name but invalid email
5. Verify you are shown a validation error message
6. Enter invalid name but valid email
7. Verify you are shown a validation error message
8. Attempt to login using various invalid names and emails
9. Verify you are shown a validation error message for each one
10. Attempt to login with valid name and email
11. Verify you are able to login
12. Verify the Login button in the global navigation bar changed to Logout
